    "description": "在沙盒战略中享受基地建设的乐趣，您可以打开或关闭敌人，还可以利用生存和塔防机制为游戏增添乐趣。<br>在可选的 “火星人 ”游戏模式中，火星人绑架了地球上最后一头奶牛，而你要把它夺回来。<br><br>无论如何，你都必须建造自动化工厂，为飞船生产材料和燃料，然后飞往月球和火星进行地球化改造。这些功能目前正在开发中。<br><br>在这款单人自动化游戏中，你要收集和管理资源、建造、自动化和扩张。一群变种人和他们的傀儡助手将为你完成所有的体力劳动。<br><br>你要塑造地形，为你的工作人员开辟道路，并为你的基地提供场所。<br>每张地图都是对高效采矿、收获和生产规划的挑战。<br><br>您还将广泛地与水打交道，因为水是能源，是生产和生长的必要资源，也是抵御火星植物攻击的有效武器。<br><br>您将体验从简单的木材到化学、原子和太空的科技时代。<br>您将建造一艘宇宙飞船，并将基地扩展到轨道、月球和火星。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features: </h2> <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 运用水强大的力量完成地形的改造，尽情释放创造力建造一个繁荣的基地。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247760/extras/7e164186369f613db1de4a3f07a5ed66.poster.avif?t=1758195901\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247760/extras/7e164186369f613db1de4a3f07a5ed66.webm?t=1758195901\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247760/extras/7e164186369f613db1de4a3f07a5ed66.mp4?t=1758195901\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li> 告别人力挖掘。不再依赖于资源矿床。利用挖掘轮来挖土，并把挖出的土运到沉积机——这台机器能够自动按照你所需的资源对土壤进行高效分类。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247760/extras/d8492907fbb6f159b6b690d5a463a990.poster.avif?t=1758195901\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247760/extras/d8492907fbb6f159b6b690d5a463a990.webm?t=1758195901\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247760/extras/d8492907fbb6f159b6b690d5a463a990.mp4?t=1758195901\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li> 用弹射器远距离运送物品。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247760/extras/7b4e681e82331d950a6d9715834c515e.poster.avif?t=1758195901\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247760/extras/7b4e681e82331d950a6d9715834c515e.webm?t=1758195901\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247760/extras/7b4e681e82331d950a6d9715834c515e.mp4?t=1758195901\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li> 注意天气变化对基地的影响。下雨会让河水水位上涨，若未能及时打开水闸，可能引发洪水。沙尘暴能为风车提供风力，但也会带来轻度干旱。做好水资源储备以应对高温。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247760/extras/3efd764c1a323f6e585b955e42aa5222.poster.avif?t=1758195901\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247760/extras/3efd764c1a323f6e585b955e42aa5222.webm?t=1758195901\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247760/extras/3efd764c1a323f6e585b955e42aa5222.mp4?t=1758195901\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></li></ul><br>沉浸于充满可能性的游戏世界中，在这里，建造、生产、收割与生态系统实现了和谐融合。",
